<HEADLINE> Online Auction Opens in Shanghai </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, July 7 (Xinhua) -- An on-line auction website was
officially opened in China's largest industrial and commercial
city of Shanghai today, attracting the participation of over 10
businesses.
</P>
<P>
The website "www.mayala.com" provides business-to-business (B-B)
and business-to-business-to-consumer (B-B-C) auction services.
</P>
<P>
