<TEXT>
<P>
"Such a test is a flagrant violation of the 1972 ABM treaty,"
Yakovlev warned.
</P>
<P>
He added that unilateral withdrawal from international treaties
by the U.S. could provoke other countries into opting out of
agreements in this field.
</P>
<P>
