<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-07 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> More Results of Wimbledon Tennis </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, July 7 (Xinhua) -- Following are more results at
Wimbledon Tennis Championships on Friday (prefix number denotes
seeding):
</P>
<P>
Men's singles semi-finals
</P>
