<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 7 (Xinhua) -- Persistence in ideological and
political work represents a long-standing principle for the
Communist Party of China (CPC) in leading the nation forward, said
a group of members of the Chinese People's Political Consultative
Conference (CPPCC) here today.
</P>
