earth. The all ordinaries hit 3281.1 in the first hour of trade
and closed one point down to 3261.0. The S&AMP;P/ASX200, closed down 1.
6 points to 3305.3.
</P>
<P>
National turnover on the ASX was 714.62 million shares traded
worth 1.67 billion Australian dollars ( 983.6 million U.S. dollars)
. There were 836 rising stocks, 669 falling and 477 were steady.
</P>
<P>
Most of the activity locally was in the National Australia Bank
and AMP.
</P>
<P>
