<HEADLINE> PLA Chief of General Staff Meets Cuban Guests </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 7 (Xinhua) -- Fu Quanyou, chief of the General
Staff of the Chinese People's Liberation Army, met here today with
Cuban Minister of Sugar Industry Ulises Rosales Del Toro.
</P>
<P>
Fu, also a member of the Central Military Commission, expressed
appreciation for the contribution made by Ulises in developing
Sino-Cuban military relations when he took the position as chief
of staff of Cuban armed forces.
</P>
