BERLIN -- Former German chancellor Helmut Kohl Thursday denied
the allegation that he had destroyed evidences of his illegal
funding scandal.
</P>
<P>
Appearing at the parliamentary hearing, Kohl blamed his
successor Gerhard Schroeder for hatching a plot to ruin his fame.
(Germany-Kohl-Allegation) 
