<HEADLINE> Peru's Economy Up 6.2 Pct </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LIMA, July 7 (Xinhua) -- Peru's gross domestic product (GDP)
grew by 6.2 percent during the first five months of this year
compared with the same period of 1999, the National Information
and Statistics Institute said Friday.
</P>
