<HEADLINE> Venezuelan Oil Price Goes Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CARACAS, July 7 (Xinhua) -- Venezuelan crude for export price
was 28.76 dollars per barrel during the July 3 to 7 week, a 0.30
dollar drop compared to the June 26 to 30 period, said Friday the
Mines and Energy Ministry (MEM).
</P>
<P>
